 Beneficiaries", "001-normal": "These sub-schemes will give benefits to the following number of beneficiaries:-", "002-table": {"column": 2, "data": [["Sub-Scheme", "Number of Beneficiaries"], ["Care-Giver Allowance", "900"], ["Student Scholarship Scheme", "140"], ["MST Free Travel Card", "700"], ["Maintenance Grant", "286"], ["Soft Loan", "5"]], "row": 6}, "003-normal": "Chief minister of Manipur has launched Chief Ministergi Shotharabasingi Tengbang (CMST) scheme on the event of International Day for Person\u2019s with disabilities held at Indoor Stadium, Lampak, Imphal. While launching this scheme, CM also provides allowances and scholarships to differently abled persons."}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Related Content", "001-normal": "\u2014 Moreover, candidates can also see the [Urban Local Bodies (ULBs) Scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/ulb-scheme-state-ranking-national-level-competition/) for Ranking of States launched by the Central Governement."}}